sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as User
    participant App as Customer App
    participant IDP as Identity Provider
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant BFF as Service BFF

    U->>App: Credentials / OAuth2 flow
    App->>IDP: OAuth2 authorization
    IDP-->>App: Session tokens (ex.: access / id)
    App->>GW: API HTTPS + token (gateway policies)
    GW->>BFF: Validated routed request
    Note over BFF: Business identity<br/>and account context
